ical to the [[Argon]] [[Mammoth]]. ==Background== This ship serves as a base ship for nearby mining vessels, which break up asteroids in the sector, retrieve any valuable resources, and then unload them at this ship. ==Physical Characteristics== This ship looks very similar to the [[M1]] [[Tokyo]], with a large saucer section on the starboard side of a long main hull. However, the MMBS's bow is a different shape, a right triangle instead of a cluster of antennae. == Combat == The MMBS can mount the [[Point Singularity Projector]] in its flank turrets, which actually gives it respectable fighting prowess. 2x rear [[SSC]] give it some anti-fighter ability as well. Even a [[M7|frigate]] must think twice before engaging one of these ships. == Equipment == As its name implies, the MMBS is designed mainly for mining. As such, it comes stock with the full set of equipment for mobile mining. In addition to combat weaponry can simultaneously mount 4x[[Mobile Drilling System|MDS]]. == Availability == This ship is a potential reward during the [[Aldrin Expansion]] plot. It can also be boarded in the form of Terran Ice Miners, which may net you an [[Ice Harvesting Facility]] in the bargain. {| style="text-align:center;" |+'''Availability''' |- style="{{Colour/Terran}}" ! Variant !![[Mars]] !! [[The Moon]] !! [[Saturn]] !! [[Terran Unknown Sector 1]] |- ! Mobile Mining Base-Ship || x || x || x || |} == Variants == A variant called Ice Miner can be found in Terran space. Can be captured to obtain Ice Mining L Facility if it happens to be carrying one. == Suggested Roles== == See Also== {{TL}} [[Category: Carrier]] {{Terran Navbox}}